					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I would recommend rewriting certain sections to correct syntax. For instance, the part referencing 4748 should be shortened a bit, as it stands out as informal. I suggest reversing the order of this section, along the lines of: &quot;due to similarities in composition and appearance, research into a possible connection to SCP-4748 in ongoing.&quot; There are other spots with minor syntax errors and the like, but it is otherwise good.</p> 
